fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 fell 20.25 points or 0.1% to settle at 19,733.55. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, fell 1.24% to 10.28. Maruti Suzuki India, Hero MotoCorp and Reliance Industries were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The August 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 31 August 2023.
